          },
          "plain_text": "Then long story short we went to the Ottolenghi restaurant and ate a cheesecake and rum fondant that blew our minds and wallet. I will confidently say that it’s made me believe that there is such thing as a good baked cheesecake. ",
          "href": null
        }
